| Real-time | **WebSocket** `/ws/chat`, `/ws/state` | Streaming tokens, animation state |
| Config | **REST** `GET/POST /settings` | CRUD for settings, memory |
| Process | Electron spawns Python child process | `child_process.spawn()` |

